WEBVTT

00:02.880 --> 00:04.760
Having a large house
is all well and good

00:04.800 --> 00:06.800
but one does tend to rattle around
in it.

00:06.840 --> 00:10.280
I was going to invite you to come and
stay there. I could help the war effort.

00:10.320 --> 00:13.000
Maybe you're talking to the wrong
people. Leave it with me.

00:13.040 --> 00:14.920
Perhaps I can make you a few new
friends.

00:14.960 --> 00:16.440
We must all help as much as we can.

00:16.480 --> 00:20.440
I have room to spare and these
poor Belgian refugees don't have
a roof over their heads.

00:20.480 --> 00:22.280
I have your money.

00:22.320 --> 00:24.320
You'll be hearing from me.

00:25.760 --> 00:28.760
He and Gabriella, they run the
restaurant for me.

00:28.800 --> 00:30.800
She's come to live with us.

00:31.680 --> 00:35.120
These are our boys. Off to fight for
king and country.

00:35.160 --> 00:37.840
Promise me one thing.
Come home to me.

